     workstation  is  about to be idle for a long period of time.
     When invoked with no arguments, it turns  the  display  off,
     waits  for  a  carriage-return  to  be typed, then turns the
     display back on again.  If invoked with any argument  except
     --nn,  bbllaacckkssccrreeeenn  turns  the  display off and exits with the
